{"tid":2123091,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020放榜] JUPAS改選排Choice諮詢區 2","createTime":"2020-07-24T11:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T01:27:45.000Z","uid":125535,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d4ba4fe897dd9a09f9256956b7b6a9ce61afed","tid":2123091,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:39:05.000Z","msg":"Post 1 在此:<br />\n[2020放榜] JUPAS改選排Choice諮詢區<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118950</a><br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>如果好急既巴絲留google form! 連登會覆得比較慢, 記得係form到揀返你改choice既時間<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/SWErfzz16XZzyCY18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FSWErfzz16XZzyCY18&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=9512a514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/SWErfzz16XZzyCY18</a><br />\n各位巴絲請耐心等候,連登上既cm都會盡快會覆返大家啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得將所有野擺返係同一層到會易啲睇,方便覆返大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n照舊恭喜大家捱咗成年終於等到今日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不論成績係你預期內定係意外都好, 都終於要面對Jupas 改choice既煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果無咩頭緒既巴絲都可以留言一齊討論,一齊搞掂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一個post集中回答JUPAS改選排Choice，等相關資訊可以集中係度，大家可以係度發問。小弟同埋背後團隊都會盡力答大家。如果想盡快得到清晰答案，建議巴絲打可以提供以下資料:<br />\nChin:<br />\nEng:<br />\nMaths:<br />\nLS:<br />\nX1: (Subject)<br />\nX2: (Subject)<br />\nX3: (Subject)<br />\nM1/2:<br />\nBest 5:<br />\n4c+2X:<br />\nA1: JSXXXX (LQ) (university)<br />\nA2: JSXXXX (LQ) (university)<br />\nA3: JSXXXX (Median/mean) (university)<br />\n<br />\n想詳細咁同我地傾既話可以係下面條拎留低問題同聯絡方法<br />\n無AC都唔緊要,可以係Google Form留低問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle Form: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/QPk8YS1mUdT4ykbV6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FQPk8YS1mUdT4ykbV6&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=653b1196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/QPk8YS1mUdT4ykbV6</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nJUPAS排序注意事項<br />\n<br />\nBand A<br />\nA1: 最想入嘅科/最想搏嘅科 (分數達LQ/LQ減1-2分)<br />\nA2: 分數達LQ嘅科<br />\nA3: 最穩陣嘅科 (達到Median/UQ以上，最好係收生人數較多嘅科，因為收生人數多，分數浮動就會少)<br />\n有人會因為自己DSE分高左，唔想浪費左個分，所以揀左D高分先入到但自己又冇興趣嘅科目，最後讀到好頹。所以各位都要諗定Plan B點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋睇返琴日記者會可以留意到今年大家成績普遍條curve都低咗,所以會多咗人揀所謂既水泡科!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時代表大家入U既機會都大咗,希望各位巴絲可以三思下自己揀既科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBand B<br />\n雖然Band B嘅取錄人數比Band A少，但都要睇清楚Band B嘅科目會唔會考慮排喺Band A以外嘅考生，唔好亂排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以上JUPAS嘅網頁 Programme Search睇下過往果科有冇收過Band B或以下嘅學生 (禁入Programme，拉落去睇Offer Statistics)<br />\nProgramme Search: <a href=\"https://www.jupas.edu.hk/tc/search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jupas.edu.hk%2Ftc%2Fsearch%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=17b4ed5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jupas.edu.hk/tc/search/</a><br />\n<br />\nBand C至Band E<br />\n都未必完全冇機會入，舊年都有近1600人被分派去Band C至Band E嘅學士學位課程，所以唔好亂放一啲明知冇可能或者完全冇興趣嘅科，浪費左個choice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05adb95a851e59f26b453126d373e996394496e4","tid":2123091,"uid":135411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"455445 phy econ <br />\nA1 js6767 hku enf<br />\nA2 js5318 ust prof acct<br />\nA3 js5300 ust b&amp;m <br />\n咁樣算穩嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA2/3 一個扎界median 一個過median 1分"},{"pid":"c9f13cd1afd5aece19da51555347b7afc72a1247","tid":2123091,"uid":210537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:19:06.000Z","msg":"445454 chem bio<br />\nA1 JSST03 東華放射<br />\nA2 JS3648 poly general nursing<br />\nA3 JSSU40 ou general nursing<br />\n咁樣排穩唔穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 已經留左第三次 前兩次冇人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日要交<br />\n唔該曬咁多位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34957b2256ebe45dd2e6987e4594fdf5129d8988","tid":2123091,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a0affb020097f2413c8b39f19d5bf7176b5ad7","tid":2123091,"uid":125535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05adb95a851e59f26b453126d373e996394496e4","tid":2123091,"uid":135411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"455445 phy econ <br />\nA1 js6767 hku enf<br />\nA2 js5318 ust prof acct<br />\nA3 js5300 ust b&amp;m <br />\n咁樣算穩嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA2/3 一個扎界median 一個過median 1分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:44:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱隔離post覆咗你~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gi